2
00:00:07,210 --> 00:00:09,430
He is not Mr. Xue.

3
00:00:09,430 --> 00:00:11,850
If it weren't for Chu Chu to find something odd,

4
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:14,700
I would still have been kept in the dark by Xue Rucheng.

5
00:00:14,700 --> 00:00:16,740
From Chang'an to Qianzhou,

6
00:00:16,740 --> 00:00:19,740
I even rushed to the military base.
[Qianzhou]

7
00:00:19,740 --> 00:00:24,530
I've suspected countless people to be the leader of those rebels.

8
00:00:24,530 --> 00:00:26,840
But I didn't suspect him.

9
00:00:29,110 --> 00:00:34,250
How can there be such a stupid judge in Tang?

10
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,880
Minister Han,

11
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,739
there are deep strangulation marks on the deceased's neck,

12
00:00:51,739 --> 00:00:54,440
from his neck to his ears.

13
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:57,150
It's for sure that he hanged himself.

14
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:02,719
All right, you are done here.

15
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:05,240
Go to the Ministry of Justice and give your statement.

16
00:01:05,240 --> 00:01:06,740
- Yes.
- Yes.

17
